Ext.data.JsonP['Uninstalling_the_debugger']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Uninstalling the debugger</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083113\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Uninstalling the debugger</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083113_Uninstallingthedebugger-Introduction\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Introduction</span></h2>\n    <p>If you need to uninstall the Aptana debugger, you can do so directly from Firefox or Internet Explorer browser.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro\">\n            <p>To update the Firefox debugger extension, please choose the menu option Tools &gt; Add-ons/Extensions, inside Firefox, and choose &quot;Update&quot;.    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083113_Uninstallingthedebugger-Instructions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Instructions</span></h2>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083113_Uninstallingthedebugger-TouninstallthedebuggerfromFirefox\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>To uninstall the debugger from Firefox</span></h3>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>From the <strong class=\" \">Tools</strong> menu in Firefox, select <strong class=\" \">Extensions</strong> to open an <strong class=\" \">Extensions</strong> pop-up window.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>On the <strong class=\" \">Extensions</strong> pop-up window, select the Debugger extension.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Uninstall</strong> button.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Close and re-start Firefox.    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>The debugger will be uninstalled the next time that you start Firefox.    </p>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083113_Uninstallingthedebugger-RelatedTopics\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Related Topics</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/About_the_Debug_perspective\">About the Debug perspective</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Installing_the_JavaScript_debugger\">Installing the JavaScript debugger</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Running_the_debugger\">Running the debugger</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Stepping_into_and_over_functions\">Stepping into and over functions</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Adding_a_breakpoint\">Adding a breakpoint</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Using_the_Console_View\">Using the Console View</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083113\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Uninstalling the debugger"});